title: Roll Away The Stone
itunes:title: Roll Away The Stone
description:
Know today that whatever you’re facing, there’s a promise to help you overcome it. There’s a promise to strengthen you. Jesus still heals. Jesus still delivers. He can still free you today by the power of the Resurrection. It’s up to us to remember the power of the Resurrection and declare His promises.Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
